::Grimmler::

Grimmler grunts as the shot hits him in the chest, sending the Maximal flying 
backwards. He jumps to his feet, firing his gun at Shockarat.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Cybertronian Fire's scanners detect gunfire outside the ship, the 
defences activating. Two missile launcher swirl around to aim at Shockarat, 
firing two signature-seeking missiles at him. The four laser batteries also 
take aim at the attacker, firing.
